Manual:Running MediaWiki on SolarisMediaWiki runs well on Solaris, but you'll need some GNU packages, which you can get:
from the Solaris install disks;
from http://www.sunfreeware.com/ (one package at a time);
via http://blastwave.org/ (a package management system, in the manner of apt or yum on Linux).
See:
Manual:Running MediaWiki on Solaris 11 / opensolaris
Manual:Running MediaWiki on Solaris 10
